  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluation of the frequency of familial cases of renal HYPODYSPLASIA
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      DNA collection from the propositus and its family. A questionnaire will be filled by the
      parents to seek other affected individual in the family.With another affected member, DNA
      collection will be collected from the whole family.

      A renal ultrasound will be prescribed for the parents, brothers and sisters.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
